* @Broomball is a sport played on ice with homemade or storebought @Broomball sticks.
* The game of @Broomball is played with 6 players from each team at once on the ice, two of which are designated goalies.
* @Broomball is played with a round ball roughly six inches or 15 centimeters in diameter.
* When the @Broomball ball crosses over the goal line completely a point is scored.
* @Broomball is commonly popular in communities where hockey is popular, though you need far less investment to play @Broomball than hockey.
